*opendnssec-1.3.6 (22 Feb 2012)

  22 Feb 2012; Marc Schiffbauer <mschiff@gentoo.org> -opendnssec-1.3.4.ebuild,
  +opendnssec-1.3.6.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.3.6. Drop old version. Thanks to Tom Hendrikx. Fixes bug
  #405295.

  25 Jan 2012; Marc Schiffbauer <mschiff@gentoo.org> opendnssec-1.3.5.ebuild:
  Support >=dev-libssofthsm-1.3.1. Thanks to Tom Hendrikx.

